wiki.summary: “Never Left” is the second promotional single off of Lil Tecca’s third mixtape, We Love You Tecca 2. Over a tropical instrumental, Tecca declares his return to hip-hop, alongside boasting the benefits of his position. The track was first previewed on March 19, 2021 via Lil Tecca’s Instagram. The track released on May 6, 2021, accompanied by a music video the following day. Read more on Last.fm.
